To use SteamST (Steam Server Tool):

1. Put in same directory as SteamCMD
2. Change all Paths to the paths you want it to install to.
3. Add Steam username and Steam password and a servername

Starting Server with Srcds:

1. Make sure you have changed the paths and have installed the Game you want to start.
2. just follow instructions on screen.

SteamST will not reboot the server the server automaticly if it crashes.

Starting Server with console:

1. Make sure you have changed the paths and have installed the Game you want to start.
2. Change the Startup instructions of the game you want to launch.
3. Just follow instructions on screen.

Console server will most of the time if it crashes automaticly reboot if not open it again with SteamST.Bat.


THis is still in Beta.

